#v2.0.0
1) Write all admin notices also to log file
2) Set default width for Logs field instead of auto line lenght
3) Cpu Limit can't be under %10
4) Add hook to reset plugin settings on deactivation
5) Fixed: Options not updating the script accordingly
          via 1) Set default values for options
          via 2) Automatically update the bash script
                 with default values when the plugin
                 is activated or reactivated.
6) Added cache_preloader.php to replicate same wget
   functionality with Wordpress HTTP API and DOMDocument
   for preloading ops for further development. Aiming to
   make plugin not depend any external bash script.

